room_title: Escape room "Escape Plan" by Conquer Escape Rooms in Sioux Falls
room_address: 310 Industrial Rd Suite A Harrisburg, SD 57032
room_description: You and your colleagues decided to travel to a third world country as part of a humanitarian aid group. While exploring the hostile territory, things took a turn for the worst. You were wrongfully arrested and thrown in prison for a crime you did not commit. Coming face to face with the reality that you will soon be executed, you devise a plan to escape your cells, contact the U.S. Embassy and break out of prison. During the next guard change, you will have one hour to execute this escape plan and try everything you can to get out alive.
